data.description: Experience the quintessential Lowcountry lifestyle in this charming classic brick ranch nestled in the sought-after Polk Village neighborhood. This meticulously redone (3) bedroom, (2) bath home exudes character and is move-in ready. The original hardwood floors have been beautifully refinished, providing a perfect canvas for your personal touch. Recent upgrades to the kitchen and bathrooms add a touch of modern convenience to this timeless gem. Enjoy outdoor living with a fenced yard, spacious front porch, convenient utility closet, inviting patio, and a convenient carport. Located just off Boundary St., this home offers easy access to restaurants, shopping, the picturesque Spanish Moss Trail, and downtown Beaufort. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity - act now! This vacant property is ready and waiting for its new owner.
